name: adidas by Stella McCartney Tote
description:
A roomy tote for training and more, made with recycled and vegan materials. You're super sporty, but not everybody has to know it. Stow your workout gear in this adidas by Stella McCartney tote, pass on the elevator and take the stairs to the gym two at a time. If anyone asks, point to the tote and tell them you got your perfectly sculpted arms by shopping.

To reduce our reliance on virgin materials, we make sure that our vegan alternatives also contain a minimum of 25% recycled content.
